<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-08-13T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-08-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="1777" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1777">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 419.11D29/102.</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Price</persName> to
                                    the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                        <hi rend="italic">Panama</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-08-13">
                                        <hi rend="italic">August 13, 1915</hi></date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>Your telegram of August 7. In addition to proposal contained in my
                                telegram of April 26, Minister for Foreign Affairs by formal note
                                agrees to let us select as arbitrator the Minister of Netherlands to
                                the United States, who is also accredited to this Government, or any
                                one of the Ambassadors from Argentina, Brazil, and Chile to the
                                United States.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Price.</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>